                    <h2>Account Info and Preferences</h2>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h5>To view your account info, click on your profile icon, then select "Account Info." Here, you can see the account information set by your department. If there is any incorrect information, please inform your administrator, as they can make the necessary changes for you.</h5>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h5>This study plan checker also features a dark mode option. To enable it, click on your profile icon and toggle the switch to activate dark mode.</h5>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h5>To log out, click on your profile icon and select "Log Out."</h5>
                    
